Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休息不用做助手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这天把助手的工作忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受私人生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 足须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得你一个人住会不会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就给你一个Morning call
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.80,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&HF87785&\3c&HFFFFFF&}足须小姐的休假日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-90\move(695,-55,695,120,0,1400)}东京漫画学院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙穗都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都看不到你 我们都想你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 因为要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起工作本身 辛苦的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你简讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因为你没有回覆我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以觉得你没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来跟工作相比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是应付老师更辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样 作出辅助线…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个部分老师已经教会我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙穗都 午餐只吃沙拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为工作时候饮食都很不均衡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个漫画家居然没有体恤沙穗都那纤瘦的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你之后有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要一起去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚你应该很忙吧 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为天气很好 所以我洗了很多内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你中午吃什么了 我是吃杯面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没有回覆我 是不是生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\bord0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(405,241)}你一个人很寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 下次再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是足须
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以为我惹你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人工作实在是太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意来 我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我也没有什么事做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我休息的时候发这么多简讯过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在有点烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种照顾个伤脑筋的孩子感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌美酱自己掀起裙子的图 很难画好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候如果有人实际做出来让我画的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人会这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.89,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H7F70F2&\3c&HFFFFFF&}不试试怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师自己来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上女性的内裤和裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再自拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 这是什么Play
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有那种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有反而是种麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都画不好 只好这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一点都不好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你的内裤我都看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情景真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个你赶快拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就拜托足须小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 为什么要我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你设定好时间 再摆姿态就好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有数码相机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机的话不能固定好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把裙子掀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个再高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想以这种形式让你看到我的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少把灯关了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能说「你很漂亮」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样 太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不过份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 我也想赶快把这种事做完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 抓住裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快掀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拍了 请你不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐这个大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么穿着裙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐这个大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
